{"id":337224,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/03/global-voices-无人机拍下的柬埔寨美景/","date":"2014-03-15T01:45:48Z","modified":"2017-12-25T13:50:40Z","title":"Global Voices | 无人机拍下的柬埔寨美景","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/serrini/10576459744/in/set-72157637125635316\"><img alt=\"Cambodian countryside\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/cambodia-trees.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>柬埔寨的乡村</p>\n</div>\n<p>在柬埔寨拍摄纪录片时，制作人<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.robertoserrini.com/\">Roberto Serrini</a>抽空前往了数个柬埔寨的城市和乡镇。他的团队用了一架DJI幻影无人机以及GoPro摄影机来捕捉柬埔寨迷人之美，他也<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://vimeo.com/82292117\">形容</a>本次拍摄过程是一场「令人赞叹的体验」：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在金边的一隅以及Anluk Leak乡村，我得以从天际俯瞰这片土地如电影般的美景。</p>\n<p>这是一趟堪称令人惊叹的体验，大多数这里的孩童没有见过播放中的电视，更遑论是一台飞行中的无人机，自他们脸中映出刺激、惊慌、赞叹、敬畏和好奇混合而出的情绪是对我而言一大乐事。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>下列是一些Roberto在Flickr上放出的柬埔寨之旅<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/serrini/sets/72157637124992066/\">照片</a>：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/serrini/10576685533/in/set-72157637125635316\"><img alt=\"A rural scenery in Cambodia\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/cambodia-mountain.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>柬埔寨乡村的景观</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/serrini/10576358183/in/set-72157637124992066\"><img alt=\"A temple in Phnom Penh, Cambodia's capital\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/phnom-penh-temple.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"352\"></a></p>\n<p>金边，柬埔寨的首都里的一座寺庙</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/serrini/10576109945/in/set-72157637124992066\"><img alt=\"A monk walking in a community plaza\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/phnom-penh-monk.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"321\"></a></p>\n<p>一位行经公共广场的僧人</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/serrini/10576094026/in/set-72157637124992066\"><img alt=\"Cambodia's tuktuk, a popular mode of transport\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/phnom-penh-trike2.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>柬埔寨的嘟嘟车是一种很受欢迎的交通工具</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/serrini/10576144994/in/set-72157637124992066/\"><img alt=\"A temple in Phnom Penh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/phnom-penh-temple2.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>金边的寺庙</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/serrini/10576354223/in/set-72157637124992066\"><img alt=\"Cambodia's tuktuk, a three-wheeled public vehicle\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/phnom-penh-trike.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>嘟嘟车，一种三轮大众运输工具</p>\n</div>\n<div>本文影片与相片拍摄为Roberto Serrini，且经许可使用。</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>译者：Josephine Liu</p>\n<p>校对：Fen</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2014/03/08/drone-footage-shows-beautiful-cambodian-landscape/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2014/03/15/13252/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br /><span><span>分享: </span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%97%A